  "texts": [
    "In the propose scheme, the authors, for the first time, moved from a simulation environment to a real test-based deployment in NDN Forwarding Daemon (NFD).",
    "To summarize their work, the authors briefly define three CPA scenarios and analyze their impact.",
    "A. Unregistered Remote Provider Scenario: In this CPA scenario, the attacker controls any nodes between the good provider and client.",
    "The attacker changes the original data in the CS and sends the poisoned data to the clients.",
    "B. Multicast Forwarding Scenario: Multicast is one of the possible forwarding strategies that is combined with the current NDN implementation (Afanasyev et al. 2014)."
  ],
